Setting up an 1176 compressor? 🎛️🎶
Here are a few things to remember:

1. Fastest attack & release settings are achieved at the HIGHEST numbers

2. The fastest attack on an 1176 is 20 MICROseconds & slowest attack is 800 MICROseconds… (Still VERY fast)

3. Release times range from 50 milliseconds - 1.1 seconds

4. The AE version of the 1176 gives you a 2:1 setting on ratio AND a “fixed” 10 millisecond attack time to let those transients through with drums and get PUNCH!
